# === About dialog comments / description ===

msgid ""
"System-wide audio enhancement for BigCommunity.\n"
"\n"
"A five-stage Rust DSP chain — BigBass (psychoacoustic bass synthesis), "
"BigClarity (treble exciter), BigSpace (Mid/Side widener), BigCross "
"(Bauer crossfeed for headphones) and BigLoud (compressor + limiter) "
"— routed through PipeWire's filter-chain. Auto-applies a tuned "
"profile when you switch output device (laptop, headphones, Bluetooth, "
"HDMI), with built-in presets ranging from Studio Reference to "
"Atmos / Cinema."
msgstr ""
"Realce de áudio para todo o sistema, do BigCommunity.\n"
"\n"
"Cadeia DSP de cinco estágios em Rust — BigBass (síntese psicoacústica "
"de grave), BigClarity (exciter de agudos), BigSpace (alargamento "
"Mid/Side), BigCross (crossfeed Bauer para fones) e BigLoud (compressor "
"+ limiter) — roteada pelo filter-chain do PipeWire. Aplica um perfil "
"afinado automaticamente ao trocar o dispositivo de saída (laptop, fones, "
"Bluetooth, HDMI), com presets prontos que vão de Referência de Estúdio "
"a Atmos / Cinema."

